---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
const updated = "2025-08-17";
---
<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy · EireQuant" description="How we handle data on eirequant.com.">
  <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p class="meta">Effective date: {updated}</p>

  <p>
    This Privacy Policy describes how EireQuant (“we”, “us”) collects and uses information when you use
    <strong>eirequant.com</strong> (the “Site”). This Site is a static website hosted on GitHub Pages.
  </p>

  <h2>What we collect</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Basic usage data:</strong> standard web logs (IP address, user-agent, pages visited) recorded by our hosting provider for security and reliability.</li>
    <li><strong>Analytics (optional):</strong> we may use a privacy-friendly analytics provider (e.g., Plausible or Cloudflare Web Analytics) to understand aggregate usage. These tools do not use invasive tracking or sell data.</li>
    <li><strong>Communications:</strong> if you email us or submit a form, we receive the information you choose to provide (e.g., name, email, message).</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>What we do not collect</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>No account creation on the Site.</li>
    <li>No advertising trackers or third-party retargeting pixels.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Cookies</h2>
  <p>
    The Site does not set cookies by default. If we enable analytics, they will operate without using
    personally identifying cookies.
  </p>

  <h2>How we use information</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Operate, maintain, and improve the Site.</li>
    <li>Monitor uptime, performance, and abuse prevention.</li>
    <li>Respond to messages you send us.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Sharing</h2>
  <p>
    We do not sell personal data. We may share minimal data with service providers who help us run the Site
    (e.g., hosting or analytics), bound by appropriate terms.
  </p>

  <h2>Data location & retention</h2>
  <p>
    The Site is hosted on GitHub Pages; logs may be processed in the UK, EU, or US depending on provider infrastructure.
    We retain logs for a limited period for security and operations.
  </p>

  <h2>Your choices</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>You may contact us to request deletion of messages you’ve sent.</li>
    <li>You can block analytics via browser settings or content blockers.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Third-party links</h2>
  <p>
    The Site may link to third-party websites. Their privacy practices are their own; please review their policies.
  </p>

  <h2>Children</h2>
  <p>
    The Site is intended for adults. We do not knowingly collect information from children.
  </p>

  <h2>Changes to this policy</h2>
  <p>
    We may update this Policy. We’ll revise the “Effective date” above and, when appropriate, provide additional notice.
  </p>

  <h2>Contact</h2>
  <p>
    Questions about this Policy? Email <a href="mailto:hello@eirequant.com">hello@eirequant.com</a>.
  </p>

  <style>
    .meta{ color:#666; margin-top:-.25rem; }
    h2{ margin-top:1rem; }
    ul{ margin-left:1rem; }
  </style>
</BaseLayout>
